{
  "texts": [
    "3 | Retrospective enrichment analysis for all models across five selected macromolecular targets.",
    "The fine-tuned models were used to rank the held-out actives and inactives of the respective protein targets.",
    "The percentage of known actives ranked per considered number of test set molecules (10, 50, 100) was computed across ten runs.",
    "Bar heights report the median across runs and error bars report the first and third quartiles (n = 10).",
    "Source data are provided as a Source Data file."
  ]
}